==============================================================================
                       MPI Contention Benchmark Suite
==============================================================================

  Author: Abhinav S Bhatele
  Date Created: November 11th, 2008
  E-mail: bhatele AT illinois.edu

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The benchmarks in this suite can be used to estimate the impact of network
topology and contention on the communication time on a supercomputer.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
COMPILE:
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  mpicxx -O2 -o lat latency.C
  mpicxx -O2 -DRANDOMNESS=0 -o nn contention.c
  mpicxx -O2 -DRANDOMNESS=1 -o rnd contention.c
  mpicxx -O2 -o hops contention_hops.C
  mpicxx -O2 -DCREATE_JOBS=0 -o line contention_jobs.C
  mpicxx -O2 -DCREATE_JOBS=1 -o jobs contention_jobs.C

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CITATION:
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Any published work which utilizes this API should include the following
reference:

"Abhinav Bhatele and Laxmikant V. Kale, Quantifying Network Contention on Large
Parallel Machines, Parallel Processing Letters (Special Issue on Large Scale
Parallel Processing), Vol. 19, Issue 4, pp. 553-572, 2009"

==============================================================================
